Executive Summary


Problem that Occurred

1. Find a good dataset - it was a challenge to find a good data set, with relevant dimension for the industries KPI’s.

2. Choosing the proper KPI’s – it is imperative to choose a right KPI’s as that will set you on the right path. Going through other projects assisted my broad knowledge of KPI’s. thus, I was able to choose KPI’s relative to my dataset.

3. DAX- (Data Analysis Expression) I encountered problems while writing DAX formula in calculating measures and column that were pertinent in building of my dashboard.
